Regular Bun: WHEAT Flour (contains Calcium Carbonate, Iron, Niacin, Thiamin), Water, Sugar, Vegetable Oil (Rapeseed), Yeast, Salt, Emulsifier (E481), WHEAT Gluten, Preservative (Calcium Propionate).

Beef Patty: 100% Pure Beef. A little salt and pepper is added to season after cooking.

Ketchup: Tomatoes, Spirit Vinegar, Sugar, Salt, Spice Extracts.

Mustard: Water, Spirit Vinegar, MUSTARD Seed, Salt, Sugar.

Onions: 100% Dehydrated Onion, rehydrated.

Pickle Slices: Gherkins, Water, Spirit Vinegar, Salt, Firming Agent (Calcium Chloride), Natural Flavouring, Preservative (Potassium Sorbate).
